      "writtenOn": "2018-01-12T18:11:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Seems like we need to ensure we\u0027re only expanding the time range. At least for Begin, we should only move Begin earlier, not later.\n\nThis matters for a situation like:\n1. I add a comment \"jennifer is following up\" and mark it flaky.\n2. Two hours later, I remove the old comment and add a new one \"skia:1234\" and again mark it flaky.\n\nThe Begin will come from the second comment rather than the first, so we\u0027ll miss 2 hours of flakiness.",
      "range": {
